        "required_age": "17",
        "is_free": false,
        "short_description": "PAYDAY 3 is the ultimate co-op FPS crime fantasy. Choose between stealth or loud playstyles, customize your character, and get ready to pull off the perfect heist.",
        "detailed_description": "<h1>YEAR 1 EDITION</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1272080/extras/3ee6025171ec4ddb30a1919f39ff4133.avif?t=1779192452\" alt=\"\"data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1272080/extras_big/3ee6025171ec4ddb30a1919f39ff4133.avif?t=1779192452 width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The <strong>PAYDAY 3: Year 1 Edition</strong> offers everything needed to get started in the heisting world. The Year 1 Edition includes all major content releases, along with the many free updates and improvements released over the game’s first year.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>It features:</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The base game Payday 3 </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Payday 3 Year 1 Pass: The Season Pass includes four major DLC bundles - Syntax Error, Boys in Blue, Houston Breakout and Fear &amp; Greed - each introducing a new heist, a variety of weapons, and numerous cosmetics.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Preacher pack (including 1 outfit, 1 weapon)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drifter pack (including 1 outfit, 1 weapon)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Heavy Hitter pack (including 1 outfit, 1 weapon)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Assassin pack (including 1 outfit, 1 weapon)</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Island skin</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dark Sterling Mask</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Skull of Liberty Mask and Golden Slate Gloves</p></li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >PAYDAY 3 is a 1-to-4 player FPS where you live out the ultimate heist fantasy. Tackle jobs in stealth to empty vaults without leaving a trace. Or charge in loud, fight off relentless enemies, and escape with the big score. A deep skill tree, extensive weapon selection and unlockable modifications provide near endless variety, no matter your playstyle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1272080/extras/cf719c8484b5105d67e6379d6c99f4ae.avif?t=1779192452\" alt=\"Legendary Heisters\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1272080/extras_big/cf719c8484b5105d67e6379d6c99f4ae.webp?t=1779192452 width=1560 height=525 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Put on the mask and become a legend. After years off the grid, the Payday Gang returns to unleash an epic crime wave across New York City. Join the world’s most infamous crew with your customized look, loadout and skills.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1272080/extras/997ae848439c3c8a7eef6d7e1dc16e88.avif?t=1779192452\" alt=\"Give in to Greed\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1272080/extras_big/997ae848439c3c8a7eef6d7e1dc16e88.webp?t=1779192452 width=1560 height=525 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this life of crime, the only limit is your own ambition. Use cash from heists and challenges to fill your armory with powerful new weapons. Unlock specialized skills and gadgets to enhance your favorite tactics. Gotta spend money to make money!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1272080/extras/15eef69f674ebe6d85062a5b463d4760.avif?t=1779192452\" alt=\"Precision or Chaos\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1272080/extras_big/15eef69f674ebe6d85062a5b463d4760.webp?t=1779192452 width=1560 height=525 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Meticulous preparation or raw violence: The choice is yours. PAYDAY gives you the tools to avoid escalation, but if the alarm goes off, the heist must go on. Cops, SWAT and Special Units will combine forces to take you out. What will your strategy be?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1272080/extras/ea71fe2080f6737b6538c6b9cc3ef730.avif?t=1779192452\" alt=\"Better Together\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1272080/extras_big/ea71fe2080f6737b6538c6b9cc3ef730.webp?t=1779192452 width=1560 height=525 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The perfect heist demands coordination. Bots will always have your back, but nothing beats a well-organized team of players. Whether you split up or stick together, you’ll need to overcome escalating threats as one. In PAYDAY 3, your crew is your greatest weapon.</p>",
